id.description: The unique identifier of the team drive.

createdDateTime.description: The date and time when the team drive was created.

description.description: A brief description of the team drive.

displayName.description: The display name of the user who last modified the team drive.

id.description: The unique identifier of the user who last modified the team drive.

lastModifiedDateTime.description: The date and time when the team drive was last modified.

name.description: The name of the team drive.

webUrl.description: The URL to access the team drive via a web browser.

driveType.description: The type of the team drive (e.g., private, public).

displayName.description: The display name of the user who created the team drive.

email.description: The email address of the group that owns the team drive.

id.description: The unique identifier of the group that owns the team drive.

displayName.description: The display name of the group that owns the team drive.

deleted.description: The amount of storage space that has been deleted from the team drive.

remaining.description: The remaining storage space available in the team drive.

state.description: The current state of the team drive's storage quota (e.g., normal, exceeded).

total.description: The total storage space allocated to the team drive.

used.description: The amount of storage space used in the team drive.
